floods occur in northwestern australia
( agence france - presse , dunshi , australia , 28th ) - at a time when drought and forest fires are trampled on in many parts of australia , floods in some remote areas of the northwestern part of the country are rampant .
today , the disaster relief authorities have to transport fresh grain supplies to the town of baoke in the kaliya bay of kunlan province , which has been blocked by floods for nearly three weeks .
baoke town is often flooded , and the past flood has caused the town to suspend its ties with the outside world for several months .
however , the head of the local parliament , tenser , said that this year , baoke town was hit by a sudden flood .
he said : " there is no fresh milk , fruits , or vegetables , and bread is also very limited . before the roads are reopened , there are only some food stocks . "
" the last truck that suddenly entered the town of baoke was trapped in the flood . the truck went into the city on the 22nd . we suspended our contacts with the outside world on the evening of the 22nd . "
tenser said that in the past few days , the water level has dropped , and if there is no continuous rain , the road will be open this week .
randt , the owner of the bar in baoke town , said that he was very careful to ensure beer supply , and that he was unable to go to the bars to drink because of the flood .
randt said : " they drink , play cards , and fish to kill time . "
" the flood has now been replaced by mud . therefore , even if the accumulation of water on the road gradually dissipated , it is still impossible to pass through . "
several hundred - year - old rugby trees to be decorated with olympic venues
( agence france - presse , athens , 28th ) - about 4,000 100 - year - old canary trees will be transferred to the 2004 olympic marathon race route and other olympic games venues .
these canary trees will be transferred from the remote islands of christchurch and the island of scaesar .
according to the athens olympic preparatory committee , these trees will be eliminated sooner or later because local construction projects will be carried out .
the athens olympics preparatory committee said that at present , these canary trees are temporarily stored and are preparing to grow 1,500 100 - year - old canary trees along the 42.2 - kilometer long marathon race route in the future .
the remaining old trees will be planted in other olympic venues .
the canary tree is a common scenic spot in greece , and the recently released olympic torch form is the shape of the canary tree , and its inspiration comes from the canary tree .
an official of the olympic preparatory committee said : " this proposal represents the sensitivity of the environmental protection of the preparatory committee . "
three million euros will be spent on greening along the marathon track .
protesters and people close to the community said that the marathon route would undermine the local environment , and some areas where the competition route goes will be widened and destroy the original scenery that has been preserved so far .
environmental protesters have also complained that many trees in some areas of athens have been rooted out because of the olympic - related road projects .
exit polls : sharon - led coalition wins israeli general election
( agence france - presse , jerusalem , 28th ) - israel held a parliamentary election today . according to the results of a poll conducted at the exit of polling stations , the right - wing coalition party led by prime minister sharon will win the election and will win 32 to 36 of the 120 seats in the parliament .
sharon 's office said that the leader of the main opposition labor party , minzana , had admitted his failure and called sharon to congratulate him .
it is estimated that the labor party will have 17 to 19 seats , lower than the original 25 , which will be the worst result of the labor party 's election since the founding of israel in 1948 .
the middle - of - the - road reform party is expected to gain a great deal from only six seats in the last parliament to 14 to 17 seats , thus threatening the status of the second largest party of the labor party .
it is expected that the party will have 9 to 13 seats , less than the current 17 seats .
the above estimates were announced by public television and private channel 2 television stations after the close of the voting at 10 pm .
united party cadres said that they had already started talks in the hope of forming a coalition government that could operate , but labor party leader minzana ruled out the possibility of joining the sharon government .
