the volunteers used rubber boats to send local residents to the shops for shopping .
government officials have also built platforms in old urban areas to facilitate people 's travel .
the historic city of cologne also avoided a robbery amid heavy rain .
a total of 144 kilometers south of cologne was forced to suspend the transportation of the river .
