xinhua news agency , xi ' an , january 8 , the work of hu xinmin , an artist of the sixth battalion in fengxiang county , shaanxi province , was chosen as the chinese sheep of the year of the sheep while being selected as the 2003 stamp .
this is the first time that the chinese people have chosen the mascot for their own new year .
starting from the end of september 2002 , the cctv and more than 50 media nationwide jointly collected the 2003 sheep 's year mascot in china .
as of the end of 2002 , the evaluation committee had received more than 300 entries for the " sheep " project .
among the " sheep " with their own characteristics , the mud - painted by shaanxi 's nongovernmental artist hu xinmin , who is " vociferous , joyful , and auspicious , " has been favored by the majority of the judges .
in the end , he won the crown of the year of the sheep with an absolute majority of votes .
the baochicken area in shaanxi province has always been known as " a village of folk arts and crafts . " in 1995 and 2002 , the pillows of the folk artists in baojiulong county and the mud and horses of the veteran artist of the six battalions village of fengxiang county , hu shen , were respectively used by the state post office as the stamp design of the year , and were issued to the people at home and abroad .
