xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 22 ( reporter le shaoyan ) the policy committee of the central bank of japan , which ended on the 22nd , decided to maintain the current financial policy and to maintain the total amount of funds provided to the market at the level of 150 - trillion yen ( 1 us dollar equals 118 - billion japanese yen ) .
the meeting held that the government and the ruling party should adopt a cautious attitude on the issue of " drawing up an appropriate inflation target . "
the meeting held that although japan 's economic prospects have become even more vague , the stock market and the financial market have been relatively stable , and there has been no major change in the economic situation , so it has decided to maintain the current financial policy .
with regard to the government and the ruling party 's demand for the central bank to further relax the monetary base and set the target of moderate inflation , the central bank believes that the japanese financial market has sufficient funds at present .
if there is a shortage of funds in the financial market in the future , the central bank will increase the amount of capital investment in accordance with the needs .
it is reported that the japanese government and the ruling party hope that the central bank will bring the annual growth rate of domestic prices to a level of 1 to 3 percent .
iraq war may lead to sufficient supply in international oil market
xinhua news agency , riyadh , january 22 , according to a report by algerian energy and mining minister al - harry on the 22 nd , the oil exporting countries ( opec ) cannot guarantee to make up for a daily shortage of 5 million barrels of crude oil in the international market if a war breaks out in iraq .
harry said that among the opec members , only saudi arabia and the arab united chiefs of staff have actual space to increase production .
he said : " opec has problems in meeting market demand because saudi arabia and the united arab emirates , which have room for increasing production , can increase output by up to 3 million barrels a day . "
since december last year , crude oil prices in the international market have continued to rise due to the threat of a large - scale strike in venezuela and the iraq war .
the organization of petroleum exporting countries ( opec ) today decided to increase oil production by 1.5 million barrels per day from february .
however , as the threat of the war in iraq has not been eliminated and britain and the united states have continued to send more troops to the gulf region , oil prices on the international market continued to rise on the 21 st .
harry said that compared with the supply and demand relations , the current international oil prices are more affected by the tense international political situation .
shenzhen and lo wu customs crack down on money smuggling
xinhua news agency report of january 25 th from shenzhen ( by staff reporter li nanling ) - ( by staff reporter li nanling ) while ensuring civilized and highly efficient supervision and control , the shenzhen lo wu customs has severely cracked down on the smuggling of money through passenger inspection channels .
last year , the customs cracked a total of 1,023 monetary cases , worth more than 150 million yuan , of which 15 cases involving more than 500,000 yuan ( excluding foreign exchange bills ) were involved .
as the largest passenger inspection port in the country , the lo wu customs is charged with the task of monitoring more than 25,000 passengers a day , and if it is not strictly controlled , there may be a considerable amount of money outflow every day .
in the face of such a situation , we should always adopt strict supervision and control measures , conduct thorough investigation , and strictly guard against the outflow of money in our country .
at about 0900 on 19 february last year , a middle - aged woman , who was carrying a baggage and flying fast , attracted the attention of the customs officers .
after the baggage was passed , customs officers found that there was a suspicious object inside the baggage , and they opened the box for examination . they found that the three big tied up with a black plastic bag was a total of 3 million hong kong dollars .
this is the largest case in which passengers have overtaken money in the past two years .
in july and august last year , " underground banks " outside the border attempted to take advantage of the summer vacation of the lo wu port to bring in a large number of passengers , and the port was in the process of renovation and the personnel on the spot were crowded with the opportunity to steal a large amount of foreign currencies into the country .
the customs has attached great importance to this , laid stress on the deployment of manpower on the spot , and resolutely cracked down on the smuggling of foreign currencies by " underground banks . "
from 2 july to 1 august , the lo wu customs cracked four cases of " underground money houses " smuggling foreign currencies , worth more than 1.46 million yuan .
tibetan lunar new year delegation visits tibet
xinhua news agency report of january 27 th from lhasa ( by staff reporter abang ciren ) - on the afternoon of the 27 th , the hall of the lhasa hotel was filled with a festive atmosphere . more than 300 people from all walks of life in tibet and from all walks of life attended the spring festival and the tibetan new year celebrations held here by the autonomous region .
at the meeting of the tibet autonomous regional people 's government , legqog , chairman of the tibet autonomous regional people 's government , extended new year greetings to the people of all nationalities throughout the region , to all the builders of the qinghai - tibet railway , to the officers and men of the people 's liberation army , the armed police , and the public security cadres and policemen stationed in tibet , and to the tibetan compatriots abroad .
he said : over the past year , with the cordial concern of the party central committee and the state council , and with the selfless support of the people of all nationalities throughout the country , especially the provinces , municipalities , and key state - owned enterprises , the autonomous regional party committee and government have united and led the people of all nationalities in the region to uphold the guiding ideology of the work in tibet at the beginning of the new century , work in unity , blaze new trails , and maintain the sustained , rapid , and healthy development of the national economy .
tibet has seen a good situation in which the government is in harmony with the people , the economy is developing , society is advancing , the people are united , the situation is stable , and the people live and work in peace and contentment .
he pointed out : the new year is the first year for tibet to comprehensively implement and implement the spirit of the 16th cpc national congress , and is also a crucial year for tibet to promote a leaping development and long - term peace and stability and lay a foundation for building a well - off society in an all - round way .
tibet will comprehensively promote the healthy and coordinated development of socialist material , political , and spiritual civilization in tibet .
at the meeting , the tibet autonomous region song and dance troupe and other units gave a wonderful performance .
pagbalha geleg namgyai , vice chairman of the npc standing committee , attended the meeting .
german association for promoting peaceful reunification celebrates eighth anniversary of president jiang 's eight - point proposal on taiwan
xinhua news agency , berlin , january 27 , the association of overseas chinese and ethnic chinese in germany issued a statement on the 26th to mark the eighth anniversary of president jiang zemin 's important speech entitled " continue to strive for the fulfillment of the great cause of the reunification of the motherland . "
the statement reviewed the course of development of cross - strait relations and many actions taken by overseas compatriots in recent years to " oppose separatism , oppose taiwan independence , and promote the peaceful reunification of the motherland , " and held that compatriots on both sides of the strait have carried out full and effective cooperation .
the statement said : president jiang zemin 's important speech is a solid foundation for the chinese people on both sides of the strait and overseas compatriots to create a benign interaction and cooperation . it has the core of adhering to the one - china principle and also the feelings of the chinese people on both sides of the strait as brothers , and it has the distinct characteristics of the times , and has a strong objective in reality , and has the flexibility , flexibility , and stability for the final solution of the problem .
the statement pointed out that president jiang 's eight - point proposal comprehensively safeguarded and represented the most fundamental interests of the chinese people on both sides of the strait and overseas compatriots .
the statement called on overseas compatriots to make new efforts to promote the reunification of the motherland .
chinese cultural festival opens in ankara
xinhua news agency , ankara , january 28 ( reporter zheng jinfa and huai chengbo ) the " chinese cultural festival " with the theme of " chinese and turkish people celebrating the spring festival of china " opened in the hall of the trade center in ankara , the capital of turkey on the evening of the 28th .
the brilliant performance of the hebei song and dance theatre , such as dance , mime , and so on , has deeply attracted more than 1,500 turkish audiences .
on the evening of the same day , many viewers came to the hall to seize the best seats .
before the performance started , the hall had already been blocked , many viewers had no choice but to stand on the corridor of the hall , and many children had to see the performance of chinese actors through the crack of the curtain .
the dance " donkeys " with hebei 's local characteristics shows the interest of a young couple on their way home by riding a donkey .
from time to time , the turkish audience burst into laughter for the excellent performance of the performers and the humorous features of the program , and waved with warm applause .
when the chinese singing actor zhai fang sang the famous turkish folk songs " mountain " , the whole audience burst into thunderous applause .
after the performance , many turkish viewers rushed to the front stage and took out paper or extended their hands to invite chinese actors to sign their names . some of them even climbed onto the stage to take a group photo with chinese actors to mark the occasion , and some turkish children left tears because they did not have the signatures or pictures of chinese actors .
a turkish girl told xinhua reporters : " i have seen such a beautiful chinese dance for the first time .
i hope that various chinese performing groups will often come to turkey to perform , so that the turkish people will have a better understanding of china 's culture . "
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) mainland tourists gradually become the main buyer of hong kong golden bank
xinhua news agency report of january 29 th from hong kong ( by staff reporter : zhou zhengfa ) - the manager of the administrative department of hong kong 's dafu golden bank , mr ku tong - fa , said that mainland visitors have become the main source of tourists for hong kong 's golden bank .
he said that during the christmas and new year holidays last year , domestic customers accounted for 30 to 40 percent of the total value of gold business , becoming the major consumer of hong kong 's gold industry .
the number of mainland visitors to hong kong increased significantly in early 2002 after the liberalisation of the restrictions on mainland visitors to visit hong kong .
last year , during the chinese new year , the may 1 labor day , the 11 th golden week , and the christmas and new year holidays , mainland tourists brought along hong kong 's retail business , especially the high - grade consumer goods market in hong kong .
relevant departments in hong kong estimate that there will be 600,000 mainland visitors coming to hong kong this year , and many businesses , especially high - grade shops , will focus their attention on how to consolidate and open up the mainland market for tourists .
the company expects its business volume to grow by 5% during the spring festival .
in order to meet the needs of mainland visitors , some companies have started to change their mode of operation and strategies , and many companies have strengthened their training in putonghua , introduced courses from time to time , and enhanced their service attitude and standard .
the old gold companies usually do not offer any discounts , but at present , as long as mainland tourists pay cash , they will enjoy preferential treatment to attract more mainland customers .
( international ) cambodian protesters burn thai embassy in cambodia
xinhua news agency , phnom penh , january 29 ( reporter lei bosong and zhang ruiling ) more than 1,000 cambodian people rushed into the thai embassy in cambodia on the evening of the 29 th to burn thai national flags and vehicles and set fire to the embassy building .
cambodian police are trying to control the situation and have dispatched several fire engines to put out the fire .
at present , the cambodian police are still unable to confirm whether there are any casualties .
the protest started on the morning of the same day in protest against a thai movie star named suwaran , who made a statement entitled " wu gothel belongs to thailand . "
after that , more and more protesters gathered in front of the thai embassy in cambodia to burn the vehicle tires , the thai national flag , and the portrait of the thai female star , and then the protesters dashed into the embassy .
according to another report , suwarnan has already made a statement to reporters in thailand , denying that he had made such remarks as " wu guandan belongs to thailand . "
( international ) france sends military police to reinforce peacekeeping forces in cote d'ivoire
xinhua news agency , paris , january 29 ( reporter wang jingcheng ) french foreign minister de villepin announced at a parliamentary hearing on the 29 th that in order to ensure the implementation of the peace agreement reached by various parties in cote d'ivoire and to strengthen the french peacekeeping force , france recently sent military police reinforcement troops to cote d'ivoire .
de villepin did not disclose the number of reinforcement troops .
however , he said that france has taken all necessary measures to ensure the safety of french nationals in cote d'ivoire .
he said that with the support of the international community , france will undertake the responsibility of supervising the implementation of the peace agreement in cote d'ivoire , and work together with all parties in cote d'ivoire to restore the authority of the country and safeguard its territorial integrity .
de villepin said that the peace agreement reached by various parties in cote d'ivoire in paris on the 24th " is the most reliable guarantee for the realization of peace and national reconciliation in cote d'ivoire . "
in order to promote the implementation of the peace agreement , he has maintained close contacts with kuwaiti president barpo and leaders of other political parties in cote d'ivoire .
he said that the flight from abidjan to paris on the 3 rd had resumed on the 29 th .
( international ) nicaragua holds rally to oppose us war against iraq
xinhua news agency , malawi , january 30 ( reporter yang wenzheng ) several hundred anti - war activists held a protest rally in front of the us embassy in nicaragua on the 30 th to strongly oppose possible us military strikes against iraq .
at the rally , the organizers of the rally , the president of the " nicaraguan association for promoting peace , " yina grelo , delivered a speech condemning the united states for attempting to launch a war of aggression against iraq in order to seize iraq 's oil .
demonstrators from the capital city of malawi and some other cities held various kinds of posters , shouting slogans such as " do not want the us war against iraq and want world peace , " and demanding that the united states immediately stop all kinds of war preparations .
in a letter to the us embassy , the demonstrators said : " let us fight together for the future of world peace , freedom , and prosperity , let us learn to respect other people 's rights , and the iraq issue should be resolved by iraq itself with the assistance of the international community . "
( international ) us personal consumer spending growth slow in 1998
xinhua news agency , washington , january 31 ( reporter wang zhenhua ) a report released by the us department of commerce on the 31 st showed that despite the relatively rapid growth in personal consumption in the united states in december last year , the annual growth rate was only the same as that of the 2001 economic recession .
in the last month of last year , consumer spending rose 0.9 percent , the biggest increase since july last year .
spending on durable goods increased by 6.1 percent , while spending on non - durable goods and services both increased by 0.2 percent .
this is a clear indication that the peak season for consumption in the united states is not brisk .
in the last quarter of last year , consumer spending , which accounted for two - thirds of the gross domestic product ( gdp ) in the united states , increased by only 1 percent , which was clearly lower than the 4.2 percent growth in the third quarter , the smallest increase since the first quarter of 1993 .
economic analysts believe that this is mainly because the united states may launch a war against iraq , the stock market has dropped sharply , and the employment market has been weak . this has also become the most important reason for the us economic slowdown in the fourth quarter .
for the whole of last year , personal consumption in the united states increased by 4.5 percent , the same as that in 2001 .
the report also showed that personal income in the united states increased by 0.4 percent in december last year .
for the whole of last year , personal income in the united states increased by 3 percent , lower than the 3.3 percent increase in 2001 .
the growth in consumer spending is higher than the growth rate of income , and the rate of savings in the united states dropped from 4.5 percent in november to 4.1 percent at the end of the year .
( international ) french troops in cote d'ivoire attacked
xinhua news agency , abidjan , january 31 , french soldiers in cote d'ivoire were attacked by local protesters at the abidjan airport on the 31 st , and about 800 youths in cote d'ivoire threw stones at french soldiers , causing serious injuries to the face of a french soldier .
the situation in cote d'ivoire has escalated since the leaders of the west african countries held talks in senegal on the civil war in cote d'ivoire .
general saito dira , who is widely respected in cote d'ivoire 's political arena , was nominated as the new prime minister at the meeting and will return to china on the 31 st to start the formation of a coalition government .
however , the " young patriot " organization , which supports cote d'ivoire president bambo , is dissatisfied with the rebels ' participation in such important posts as defense and home affairs minister in the future government .
they accused france of forcing barbo to accept the government 's plan to form a cabinet , saying that dira was the " french prime minister , " and threatened that his death was waiting for diarra .
it is reported that although the runway of the abidjan airport has been cleaned up , hundreds of " young patriots " members are still staying in the waiting hall and are preparing to resist the return of delay .
the civil war in cote d'ivoire has been going on for four months and hundreds of people have died in the conflict .
the french foreign ministry today proposed the withdrawal of 16,000 french nationals in cote d'ivoire as soon as possible .
( international ) canadian astronauts will suffer setbacks in space flight plan
xinhua news agency , ottawa , february 3 ( reporter hu guangyao ) according to local media reports on the 3 rd , due to the crash of the us " columbia " space plane , the plan of two canadian astronauts to take off from the us space shuttle in may and november this year will suffer setbacks .
canada 's space agency director and canada 's first astronaut , garcia , said that the us investigation of the " columbia " incident may obstruct the missions set by the international space station , and some plans may be postponed or even cancelled .
canadian astronauts mcmullin and williams were originally scheduled to take off in may and november respectively .
both of them are currently undergoing training in houston .
three astronauts from canada took part in space flight missions by the " columbia " space plane in the 1990s .
garcia also revealed that the space science experiments carried by the " columbia " included two scientific research projects sponsored by canada .
these studies involve the growth of protein crystal , one of which is for the treatment of breast cancer and front - line cancer .
according to another report , after the " columbia " accident , the us space agency immediately shortened a training activity for astronauts in canada .
seven astronauts , who were trained at a military base near quebec , canada last week , returned to the united states after completing their training .
u.s. construction spending up in december
xinhua news agency , washington , february 3 ( reporter he ying ) the us commerce department released a report on the 3 rd , saying that us construction spending in december last year was 1.2 percent higher than in november , and the seasonally adjusted annual rate was 858.3 billion us dollars .
the report said that the seasonally adjusted annual rate of housing construction spending in december was 4.346 billion u.s. dollars , an increase of 2.9 percent over november .
analysts believe that low interest rates are an important factor in the strong growth of housing construction .
at present , the federal reserve has kept short - term interest rates at 1.2 percent , the lowest in 41 years .
however , in contrast with the housing construction , the seasonally adjusted annual rate of u.s. commerce and construction spending in december was 158.6 billion u.s. dollars , down 1.9 percent from the previous month .
analysts believe that there are factors of instability in the future of the us economy , and enterprises are unwilling to invest more in the construction of factories and other facilities .
in addition , the worry about terrorist attacks has also had an adverse impact on commercial construction activities . although bush signed a terrorist insurance bill in november last year , it is not enough to eliminate investors ' worries .
for the whole year of last year , the growth rate of housing construction spending in the united states dropped from 2.7 percent in 2001 to 0.4 percent , the lowest since 1991 .
( international ) un inspectors discover another air chemical warhead in iraq
xinhua news agency , baghdad , february 4 ( reporter wang bo and liang youchang ) - the spokesman of the un weapons inspection group , zhulanhong , said in a news release on the 4 th that the inspectors found another air chemical warhead during an inspection of a suspicious place in iraq on the same day .
the chemical warhead was found by the inspectors at the taj ammunition depot in the northern suburbs of baghdad , he said .
the warhead was labelled and kept in good condition .
he said the warhead was similar to the 12 air chemical warheads found by the inspectors in a military depot in southern iraq on january 16 .
shortly after the inspectors discovered the chemical warheads , the iraqi side announced the discovery of four similar warheads in the taj area and handed them over to the inspectors .
when briefing the security council on the inspection situation on january 27 , the chairman of the un inspection , monitoring , and inspection commission , blix , said that the iraqi government should take the initiative to give an account of these air and chemical warheads in its arms report , and should not be found by the inspectors .
on the same day , inspectors also inspected seven locations near baghdad , including a water purification facility , an agricultural chemical plant , two missile factories , and a center used to develop chemical weapons .
on the 4 th , inspectors in the northern iraqi city of mosul inspected a sugar factory and an entrustment factory .
shanghai police confirm two pilots of french airlines were turkish men
xinhua news agency report of february 10 th from shanghai ( by staff reporter yang jinzhi and yang yong hon ) - through fingerprint comparison , the shanghai police confirmed that the two men who crashed on january 23 from the french airline , the f - 112 , were turkish residents , namely , the 20 - year - old karachi state and the 19 - year - old ou zuman .
at 1058 on the morning of 23 january , the shanghai municipal public security bureau received a " 110 " report , saying that an air crash occurred in the village of the old port town of nanhui district , and two foreign men fell from a plane that was flying from the south to the north to prepare for landing .
after on - the - spot investigation and investigation , the shanghai police quickly made an appraisal and confirmed that the deceased had crashed into the cabin of the flight faff 112 from the air , and this conclusion was confirmed by the french air force .
after that , the shanghai police carried out cooperation and investigation with the french and turkish consulate general in shanghai and the police of the above two countries .
in early february , according to the remains of the two deceased at the scene and the information provided by the turkish police , such as the fingerprints and identity cards of the deceased , the shanghai police , through technical comparison , identified the same fingerprints , and finally confirmed the true identity of the two deceased .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) macao 's budget surplus 13 percent last year
xinhua news agency , macao , february 10 ( reporter li jie ) - according to information from the macao special administrative region ( sar ) government , macao 's fiscal budget for 2002 has been carried out well , with a total surplus of 1.7 billion patched in the whole year , equivalent to 13 percent of the annual budget .
it is reported that macao 's budget for 2002 was originally a deficit budget , with a deficit of 870 million yuan .
after balancing the surplus in 2001 , another 300 million macao dollars is expected to be used to make up for the surplus .
however , in the course of implementing the plan , the sar government has increased revenue and expenditure , and the actual income has increased by about 10 percent over the budget , and the actual expenditure has decreased by 8 percent compared with the budget .
financial secretary ai weili said : the increase in macao 's fiscal budget for 2002 was mainly due to the successful opening up of the gambling and gambling industries , the telecommunications industry , and the recovery of the real estate industry .
statistics show that in 2002 , there was a marked increase in the tax revenue on betting , a big rise in the number of people in the telecommunications industry , and a brisk property market , and the increase in the stamp duty on real estate transfer alone was 30 percent .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) macao passes bill to avoid double taxation
xinhua news agency , macao , february 11 , the legislative council of the macao special administrative region ( sar ) today passed a bill to empower the chief executive of the macao special administrative region ( sar ) to sign an agreement on the avoidance of double taxation .
the so - called " double taxation " refers to the same or similar tax levied by two or more tax jurisdictions on the same taxpayers , the same time and the same duty payable .
the bill is of the view that once there is a double taxation situation in macao , the chief executive of the hksar has the right to take necessary measures to regulate the situation until the signing of an inter - district agreement on the avoidance of double taxation .
members of the legislative council who are responsible for examining the " tax system in the international or inter - district double taxation situation " said that the trend of global economic integration is becoming more and more obvious , and the tax system must keep up as soon as possible , otherwise the flow of funds , commodities , and personnel will be restricted .
macao and other regions need to sign an agreement on avoiding double taxation , which is conducive to attracting foreign investment and also to macao 's foreign investment , and is an important link in promoting economic development .
it is reported that macao and portugal have already reached a double taxation agreement , and the signing of the agreement with the mainland is under discussion , and it is expected that an agreement can be reached in the middle of this year .
( fax from hometown of overseas chinese ) quanzhou becomes " china 's daily necessities production base "
xinhua news agency , fuzhou , february 12 ( reporter wang fanfan ) - quanzhou , a region with relatively rapid development of china 's private economy , has recently become a " china 's daily necessities production base , " and relevant departments recently held a grand ceremony to give a license and celebrate the occasion .
the one who won the title of " china 's daily necessities production base " is a new town in the province , a new town located in the central part of the city of nanan , the hometown of national hero zheng chenggong , and a coastal economic development zone in southern fujian .
founded in 1999 , the town has a total area of 61 square kilometers and has 11 administrative villages with a population of 45,000 , and has more than 20,000 overseas chinese , hong kong , macao , and taiwan compatriots .
at present , the province 's new town has formed a complete industrial chain with daily necessities as the mainstay .
there are more than 70 enterprises with daily necessities in the whole town , with fixed assets reaching more than 300 million yuan , and more than 10,000 people engaged in the production and supply and marketing of daily necessities , with an annual export volume of nearly 200 million yuan .
the main products include various kinds of thin film packaging bags , color bags , payees , food , and other products , as well as women 's health scarves , baby trousers , meal tissue , knitting , and children 's outdoor products , and hundreds of varieties and specifications of products , and are sold in various parts of the country as well as countries and regions such as the united states , canada , europe , and southeast asia .
in 2002 , the output value of the township 's daily - use industry reached 50.4 billion yuan , accounting for 70 percent of the total industrial output value of the whole town , and the amount of industrial and commercial taxes paid was 140.08 million yuan , accounting for 67.1 percent of the total tax revenue of the whole town .
( international ) france puts forward proposals to un security council on strengthening inspection of iraq
xinhua news agency , united nations , february 11 ( reporter guo lijun ) the french permanent mission to the united nations on the 11 th distributed an unofficial proposal to members of the un security council on strengthening the inspection of weapons in iraq .
france suggested that in the near future , the official personnel for the current stage of weapons inspection in iraq should be doubled , and that the number of inspectors should be gradually increased and the number of the inspectors should reach the current three times .
currently , there are about 110 official inspectors in iraq .
france also suggested that through strengthening air reconnaissance or using un security guards to ensure the " freeze " of suspicious locations in iraq , it should use mobile customs inspection teams to step up inspection of iraqi goods entering the country .
at the same time , france proposes to set up a new intelligence agency in new york to coordinate the actions of various countries to provide intelligence to the un monitoring , verification , and inspection commission and the international atomic energy agency .
he called on the two organizations to take the importance of the disarmament task that has not yet been completed in iraq as a sequence .
in iraq , it will arrange a liaison officer responsible for daily communication with the iraqi government .
france distributed its proposals in the form of " non - document . "
during the course of consultations on resolution 1441 , both france and russia expressed their views in this form .
according to the relevant provisions of the security council , the official nature of this " non - document " is weaker than the draft resolution , but it can be upgraded to the draft at any time at the request of the proposed country .
diplomatic sources here said that france 's proposal did not exceed the content of the speech made by its foreign minister de villepin after listening to the us secretary of state colin powell 's intelligence briefing on 5 april . this " non - document " is a summary and training of france 's stand on the issue of inspecting iraq at the request of some un security council members .
( hong kong , macao , taiwan ) mainland tourists have strong consumption capacity in macao
xinhua news agency , macao , february 14 ( reporter li jie ) in recent years , the number of tourists from the mainland coming to macao has not only increased , but also increased the consumption power .
according to the official statistics released by the macao special administrative region ( sar ) government , foreign tourists spent 4.7 billion patters in macao in the fourth quarter of last year , of which tourists from the mainland accounted for 3.3 billion patters , ranking first among tourists from all walks of life .
since the mainland relaxed its policy on outbound tourism last year , the number of mainland tourists participating in " hong kong and macao tours " and " overseas tours " outside hong kong and macao has increased rapidly .
of the 1.53 million tourists received by macao last year , 4.24 million were from the mainland , and the number of visitors to macao exceeded that of hong kong for the first time in the fourth quarter of last year , making macao the largest source of tourists .
although the average number of tourists in macao is only 28.8 hours , the average consumption per person is 2,560 patters , 64 percent higher than the average number of tourists from all over the country .
the analysis showed that jewellery , watches and clothing accessories were the most popular items purchased by tourists from all over the country , accounting for 27% and 23% of their spending in australia .
in non - shopping consumption , the average amount of consumption per person , including betting , is 837 patters , and the amount of food and accommodation is two major items , accounting for 41 percent and 36 percent respectively .
( international ) study finds early childhood learning barriers overcome
xinhua news agency , washington , february 15 ,
researchers at yale university in the united states recently found that with the growth of age , the obstacles to learning can be overcome .
the study confirmed that the nerve system of children with a weight of less than 1,500 grams is prone to problems , of which as high as 50 percent require special assistant when they go to school .
although many experiments have shown that animals can recover from early brain injuries , there has never been any report on the restoration of early brain injuries .
according to reports by the media here , researchers at yale university have followed and observed 300 early - birth children . they have conducted intellectual tests at the age of three , four and a half , six , and eight . they have found that the majority of people are constantly improving their ability to study with the passage of time .
the test said that early birth , which was classified as an " intellectual barrier " at the age of three , reached a general level in the language understanding and intelligence test five years later .
however , 23 percent of the babies are still suffering serious brain injuries due to mental bleeding , and the situation of intellectual development has never changed .
researchers said that a key factor in the development of early childhood intelligence is the family environment .
children 's intelligence from three families and their mothers who have received higher education have a higher score .
japan 's bell 's investment and development network in shenyang
xinhua news agency report of february 16 th from shenyang ( by staff reporter shi qingwei ) - the japanese bell network company recently signed an agreement with the management committee of the funan new area of shenyang city to establish a joint venture with a plan to invest 3 billion yen in the development of software and hardware for the network telephone in the new area of the southern part of the city .
it is reported that the first - phase construction project of the joint venture will be completed between april 2003 and march 2005 , and by 2005 , the number of staff and workers of the enterprise will reach 3,000 , and will become an important development and production base for the software and hardware of the network telephone in northern china .
relevant experts believe that china 's network telephone technology is still at the stage of development , and that japan 's bell network corporation is at the world 's leading level in this field , and that the project has a relatively good development prospect in china .
founded in 1989 , the japan bell network corporation is a newly emerging internet enterprise in japan . it is mainly engaged in the development , production , and network communications services of computer network software and telephone . last year , it sold a total of 12.4 billion yen .
shenyang city , liaoning province , is the economic center of northeast china .
wang xiangkun , vice mayor of shenyang city , said that the development of the southern part of china is an important it industrial base in northern china , and more and more foreign it enterprises have settled down in the southern part of the country .
( international ) china and chile sign memorandum on measures to implement animal and plant health
xinhua news agency , santiago , february 17 ( reporter hou yaoqi ) china 's state administration of quality supervision , inspection , and quarantine and the chilean ministry of agriculture signed a memorandum here on the " agreement on the implementation of health and plant hygiene measures . "
according to the memorandum , china and chile will formulate the requirements for the inspection and quarantine of imported and exported animals and plants , animal and plant products , and food products in accordance with the rules of the agreement and the standards formulated by the world animal health organization , the " international convention on the protection of plants , " and the food codes committee .
the memorandum stipulates that the two sides should strictly abide by the protocol signed by the two countries or the inspection and quarantine requirements agreed upon by the two countries , carry out inspection and quarantine work on the import and export of animals and plants , animal and plant products , and food , strengthen the efforts to resolve the issue of market access for animals and plants , animal and plant products , and food on a scientific basis , and carry the inspection and quarantine certificate issued by the export side .
the mou was signed by ge zhirong , deputy director of the state administration of quality supervision , inspection , and quarantine , and barrela , acting minister of agriculture of chile .
euro zone sees trade surplus of 102.3 billion euros
xinhua news agency , brussels , february 19 ( reporter feng jian ) the latest statistics released by the european union statistics bureau on the 19 th showed that the euro zone 's foreign trade surplus in 2002 was 102.3 billion euros , more than double that of the previous year , due to a big drop in imports .
the statistics show that the euro zone 's trade surplus in 2001 was 49.5 billion euros .
last year , the trade surplus of the 15 eu countries was 6.1 billion euros .
the report said that the sharp decline in imports was the main reason for the growth of the trade surplus .
according to statistics , compared with 2001 , the total imports of the euro zone and the eu dropped by 4 percent , while exports increased by 1 percent .
in the first 11 months of 2002 , imports from japan and the united states dropped by 12 percent and 11 percent respectively , while exports to japan and switzerland also fell by 6 percent .
among the eu member states , the biggest trade surplus was germany , with a trade surplus of 117.9 billion euros , while the united kingdom was the largest among the eu member states with a trade deficit of 63.6 billion euros .
shanghai , zhejiang and fujian financial cases drop to 13 - year low
xinhua news agency , shanghai , february 20 ( reporter wang hongyang ) the number of financial cases in the two provinces and one city of shanghai , zhejiang , and fujian , which are located at the forefront of china 's financial and trade center and the opening up of financial reform and opening up , decreased by 44.4% compared with the previous year , the amount of money involved in the cases decreased by 22.8% , and the number of cases dropped to the lowest point in 13 years .
according to the latest news from the shanghai branch of the people 's bank of china , in recent years , the financial sector in various localities of shanghai , zhejiang , and fujian has comprehensively improved the system of investigating and handling financial cases and preventing financial cases , effectively checked the trend of the high incidence of financial law and discipline violations , and the good situation of the number of cases , the amount of money involved , and the number of major and serious cases , and the number of crimes committed in the same year .
statistics show that compared with the previous year , the number of financial cases in the two provinces and one municipality decreased by 22.9 percent and 35.4 percent respectively in 1999 and 2000 , the amount of money involved in the cases decreased by 41 percent and 11.2 percent respectively , and the amount of money involved in the cases decreased by 35.4 percent in 2001 .
it has been learned that various localities in shanghai , zhejiang , and fujian have successively established a five - dimensional case prevention system that is suited to the characteristics of the local financial sector , namely , " investigation , handling , education , reform , establishment , and supervision , " and at the same time , they have formed a socialized network for the prevention of financial cases in coordination with the business functional departments , supervision departments , and local judicial organs of various banks , insurance , and securities companies .
( international ) eu stops beef imports from paraguay
xinhua news agency , buenos aires , february 20 ( reporter shen an ) the european union ( eu ) has decided to suspend the import of beef from paraguay because of the foot - and - mouth disease in paraguay .
the decision was made at a meeting of the european union ( eu ) here today , according to a report from the paraguay media .
in early february , the report submitted by the european commission 's food and veterinary office 's inspection team after its inspection of paraguay held that the measures taken by paraguay to control the foot - and - mouth disease are still not sufficient , and there are " serious problems " in the monitoring and inspection system of the foot - and - mouth disease , and it does not meet the requirements of the eu in terms of health control , professional and technical level , or export license system .
paraguay , the first case of foot - and - mouth disease in october last year , has taken preventive and control measures with the assistance of other member countries of the southern common market .
paraguay exports about 60,000 tons of beef each year , mainly to brazil , chile , and other countries .
these countries have suspended imports of beef from paraguay .
from january to october last year , the eu imported 567 tons of beef from paraguay .
( international ) austrian researchers discover polio cells that cause chronic pain
xinhua news agency , vienna , february 20 ( reporter lin chuan ) researchers at vienna university of austria found a group of nerve cells with lasting memory in human polio , and these cells will be greatly inspired by pain , and this has taken a step forward in looking for the cause of chronic pain .
the chronic patients are extremely sensitive to the pain and eventually have to endure the pain in their daily life .
however , people are almost at all aware of the causes of the disease .
according to a report by the austrian news agency , the research group led by the director of the department of nerve science of the vienna university 's institute of brain science , yu gengen , found that some polio cells did not show any unusual performance under normal conditions and would be excited after being stimulated by pain .
if the pain is strongly stimulated , the reaction will increase .
but what is different from other nerve cells is that this group of polio cells will become too sensitive to pain stimulation , and even if it is only slightly stimulated , it will be greatly affected .
researchers also found that there is a special channel in the polio cells , and when the cells are stimulated , these channels will be opened , calcium plasma will flow into the cells , which will further trigger chain reaction .
the reason why the chronic patients were too sensitive to minor pain was that the nerve cells in the polio had a lasting memory and the " pain mark " was preserved .
he said that this discovery can guide people to look for ways to eliminate this memory .
china 's consumer prices rise in january
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 21 ( reporter liu dongkai ) according to a monthly report released by the state statistics bureau on the 21 st , the overall consumer price level of chinese residents rose 0.4 percent in january over the same month last year , the first increase in the past 12 months against the background of a continuous decline in the same period last year .
the state statistical bureau said that the main reason for the increase in the overall consumer price level was that the spring festival was held at the end of january this year , and that the spring festival of february last year was different from the peak period of the festive season , so there was a certain inestimable factor .
another reason is that this year 's weather is cold compared with last year .
of the 31 provinces , municipalities , and autonomous regions surveyed in china , 22 have seen a rise in the overall consumer price level over the same period last year , and the remaining seven have dropped compared with the same period last year .
statistics show that among various categories of consumer goods , the prices of seasonal consumer goods and services , such as fresh vegetables , fresh fruits , and cultural entertainment , have risen , while the prices of grain , clothing , and durable consumer goods , which have a bearing on the long - term consumption trend , are declining .
the rise in gasoline and diesel prices has pushed up the price of liquefied petroleum gas , which has continued to rise in housing prices .
chinese tv series on middle and primary school education published
xinhua news agency , haikou , february 21 ( zhang chuanxuan and liu wei ) china 's first " lecture on the knowledge of middle and primary school education " was recently broadcast in haikou , which has evoked strong repercussions among teachers and students .
this series of sex education films published by the hainan provincial electronic audio - video publishing house are divided into primary and middle schools and middle schools .
according to different age groups , it has introduced sex knowledge in a gradual and orderly manner , including the youth spring festival , pregnancy , birth , aids protection , and sexual psychology , and has answered questions in the minds of the children with vivid music and painting .
at the first broadcast held at hainan 's zhenfa school , more than 100 people were seriously watching and quiet .
at the beginning , many girls only lowered their heads to read books , refused to raise their heads , and later gradually and frankly watched the pictures .
lai ruixing , president of this middle school , said that the school needs such a sex education teaching material , and it has solved the embarrassment of the teachers in choosing to speak and the students in stealing .
the production of this series of films has also been endorsed by relevant departments .
in november 2002 , the television series " lectures on the knowledge of middle and primary school education " won the 10th china population and culture award presented by the state family planning commission and the china population and culture promotion association .
chinese citizens to travel to malta , egypt
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 22 ( reporter qian chunxian ) the reporter learned on the 22 nd that the first delegation of chinese citizens visiting malta will leave here on march 28 .
chinese tourists can travel across the two continents within 10 days .
at that time , tourists can take off from beijing by plane of the egyptian airlines , and tour cairo for five days before flying to malta .
it is estimated that the entire 10 - day trip will cost about 16,000 yuan .
malta is located in southern europe and is close to italy .
the scenery of the blue sea and blue sky and the warm climate of the central sea have made it a famous tourist attraction in the world .
egypt is one of the four ancient civilizations in the world , and its long history has attracted tourists from all over the world .
malta became the first european country for chinese citizens to travel at their own expense in 2001 , and egypt became africa 's first target country for chinese citizens to travel at their own expense in 2002 .
egyptian airlines officially opened its first direct flight route from cairo to beijing in january this year .
the first delegation was jointly launched by the malta national tourism administration , the egyptian tourism bureau , and the guangzhou international travel agency .
( international ) blix urges iraq to start destroying the " sarmott " missile within a week
xinhua news agency , united nations , february 22 , according to a report by the media here on the 22nd , the chairman of the un monitoring , verification and inspection commission ( monitoring and inspection commission ) , hanks , has issued an ultimatum to iraq , asking iraq to start destroying its " sarmott " missile within a week .
a spokesman for the un monitoring and control council said that blix has issued this ultimatum to the un permanent representative to the united nations , mohammad al - bashir , asking iraq to start destroying the banned weapons before march 1 .
copies of the ultimatum have been submitted to the un security council .
relevant experts believe that this ultimatum has put iraqi president saddam in a dilemma .
the destruction of these missiles will make iraq lose its important weapons to defend against us attacks , and the refusal of the ipcc 's request will enable the united states and britain to have more excuses to take military action against iraq .
in the second report on the inspection of iraqi weapons submitted to the un security council on 14 february , blix and iaea director general elbaradei said that after the appraisal of the un missile experts , the range of the " sam " missile has exceeded 150 km , thus violating the relevant resolutions of the un security council .
( international ) georgian president stressed that he would try to prevent chechen illegal armed forces from entering the panjixi valley
xinhua news agency , moscow , february 24 ( reporter dong longjiang ) - in his speech at the georgian national radio station on the 24 th , georgian president shevardnadze stressed that the primary task of georgia 's powerful departments at present is to prevent and completely stop the chechen illegal armed elements from entering the panjixi valley .
he said : in a special operation launched last autumn by the georgian interior forces , police , security departments , and defense ministry , the foreign armed groups that had sneaked into the pankxi valley have been cleaned up . however , it cannot be ruled out that some illegal armed elements continue to hide in the pankexi valley in the capacity of refugees .
he said that georgia 's strong departments are capable of discovering these illegal armed elements .
at the same time , he also announced that georgia 's powerful departments will continue to carry out a crackdown on illegal armed forces in the pankexi valley in the near future .
in his speech , shevardnadze stressed the importance of cooperation and exchange of intelligence with russia and the united states on this issue .
located in georgia , the panjixixia valley is adjacent to the chechen region of russia .
russia believes that there are a large number of chechen illegal militants hiding in the pankasixia valley and accused georgia of providing asylum to them .
last year , the relations between russia and georgia were once tense due to the issue of the pankexi valley .
( international ) us and british proposals to attack iraq lead to new york stock market falling again
xinhua news agency , new york , february 24 , the three major stock indexes of the new york stock exchange fell sharply on february 24 , setting a new high since january 30 , as the united states and britain insisted on submitting a new military attack on iraq to the un security council .
in addition , the latest report on us retail sales shows that us retail sales in february are not optimistic , and this news has further affected investors ' confidence .
the dow jones industrial average fell 159.87 at 785.24 , and the technology heavy nasdaq composite index fell 26.64 at 1322.38 , and the standard & poor 's 500 index fell 15.59 at 8,332.58 .
the russell 2000 index of smaller companies was down by a big margin on the new york stock exchange , but the russell 2000 index of smaller companies rose 0.43 at 434.59 .
declining issues outnumbered advancers by a 5 - to - 2 margin on the new york stock exchange , with the volume of transactions falling to 1.53 billion shares from 1.71 billion in the previous session .
china 's red cross society raises funds for disaster areas in xinjiang
xinhua news agency , beijing , february 25 ( reporter wu jing ) the china red cross society opened a donation telephone and a donation account on the 25 th , calling on all walks of life at home and abroad to extend assistance to help xinjiang compatriots who were hit by the earthquake on the 24 th .
china red cross donated telephone number : 010 - 6513999 ( 24 - hour duty )
account number : bank of industry and commerce east and south branch of bank of china 000000009144132 - 52
the red cross society of china has urgently allocated 250,000 yuan to the disaster areas in xinjiang after the earthquake on the 24 th , and sent a disaster relief work team to the disaster areas on the 25 th .
on the 24 th , an earthquake measuring 6.8 on the richter scale hit jiashi prefecture in southern xinjiang .
by the early morning of the 25 th , the number of deaths had increased to 261 , with 2,050 seriously injured , and 8,861 families collapsed .
at present , the temperature at night in the disaster areas is about 2 degrees celsius below zero , and the disaster victims urgently need food and warm materials .
( international ) brazil 's national risk index down
xinhua news agency , brasilia , february 27 ( reporter yang limin ) the brazilian national risk index fell 2.37% from the previous day to 1,191 on the 27th .
this is the first time in eight months that the index has dropped below 1,200 points since the financial turmoil broke out in brazil in june last year .
at the same time , brazilian bonds on the international market rose 0.42 percent to 74 percent .
this is also the best record in eight months .
the national risk index is closely related to bond prices , the higher the index , and the lower the bond price .
last year , the national risk index exceeded 2,400 points , and bond prices fell to 48 percent of the face value .
since the new government took office this year , the national risk index in brazil has continued to drop .
recently , foreign investors believe that the price of bonds in brazil is low and the rate of return is high , and the demand for bonds has increased by a large margin , which has accelerated the decline of the national risk index .
however , analysts pointed out that although international investors are optimistic about brazilian bonds at present , if the us - iraq war breaks out , foreign investment will decrease , the national risk index may rise again , and the bond price will drop again .
